body.description: SPECIFICATIONS The W10518394 W10134009 Dishwasher Heating Element Kit is used to create heat during the dry cycle and increase water temperature during portions of the wash cycle when certain options are selected. If your dishes are not drying or the water in the dishwasher is not getting hot you may need to replace the element. This kit includes the heater, two heater fasteners. Please remember to disconnect the power before starting the repair. Use a multi-meter to test your heating element for continuity to determine whether this is the part that is causing your symptom. This part does not include any washers. To make your repair, disconnect the wires from the bottom of the element in the back, remove the plastic nuts holding it in place, remove the element, and repeat these steps in reverse order to install your new part. This is an easy repair that requires only a screwdriver, wrench set, and should take less than 30 minutes. Fixes the following symptoms Not drying dishes properly Not cleaning dishes properly Will Not Start Leaking Replaces part numbers:W10518394, 8194250, 8563007, 8572861, W10134009, W10441445, W10518394VP, 2977737, AP5690151, PS8260087, EAP8260087 Works with the following Whirlpool, Kenmore, Maytag, Amana dishwasher models: Kenmore: 66213032K112, 66512413N410, 66512093K210, 66512723K310, 66513002N510, 66513012K110, 66513019K111, etc. Whirlpool: 7DU1100XTSQ0, 7DU1100XTSS1, 7GU2300XTVQ2, 7GU2455XTSS0, 7WDF530PAYM0, 7WDT770PAYM0, 7WDT770PAYM1, 7WDT770PAYM2, 7WDT770PAYM3 7WDT770PAYW1, 7WDT770PAYW2, 7WDT770PAYW3, 7WDT770PAYW4, etc. Amana: ADB1100AWB0, ADB1100AWB1, ADB1100AWB2, ADB1100AWB3, ADB1100AWS4, ADB1100AWS5, ADB1100AWW0, ADB1100AWW1, ADB1100AWW2, ADB1300AFB1, ADB1300AFS0, ADB1300AFW0, ADB1400AGB1, etc. Maytag: ADB1400AGB3, ADB1400AGW3, MDB4409PAB0, MDB4409PAB1, MDB4409PAS1, MDB4409PAS2, MDB4409PAW0, MDB4630AWB1, MDB4630AWS2, MDB4630AWW3, MDB4709AWB4, MDB4709AWQ4, MDB4709AWS4, etc. Count on our W10518394 W10134009 Dishwasher Heating Element Kit part for an unrivaled mix of durability, convenient functionality, and great value for money.
